705392f-a.title: Brooklyn: Lawrence Street - Johnson Street
705392f-a.text:
Lawrence Street, west side, south of Johnson Street, showing Lawrence
Street entrance and side view of Mayflower Branch of Plymouth Congregational
Church.
July 1, 1934.
P. L. Sperr.
